# VektaDev Project Rules

## Git Workflow
After making code changes, always run:
```bash
git add . && git commit -m "descriptive message" && git push
```
This project auto-deploys to Vercel on push.

## Translations (IMPORTANT!)
This project has 4 languages. All text/copy changes must be updated in ALL files:
- messages/pl.json (Polish - default locale)
- messages/en.json (English)
- messages/de.json (German)
- messages/fr.json (French)

Never hardcode text in components - always use translations via useTranslations() hook.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14 with App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- next-intl for internationalization
- Framer Motion for animations (use LazyMotion for performance)

## Project Structure
- /src/app/[locale]/ - Pages with locale routing
- /src/components/ - Reusable components
- /src/i18n/ - Internationalization config
- /messages/ - Translation JSON files

